# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# EVAR Planner — patient data and runtime artefacts must NEVER be
# tracked. The phantom files are the only library entries that ship
# with the repo (they're synthetic).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Patient image data ----------------------------------------
# Ignore everything under data/ EXCEPT the non-PHI AortaSeg24 class-label
# map (a paper-derived id→name→pipeline_label table the code loads at
# runtime; contains no patient data). Using data/* (not data/) so the
# single-file re-include below is honoured.
data/*
!data/aortaseg24_class_map.json
!data/setA_class_map.json
!data/setA_slicer_colors.ctbl
*.dcm
*.DCM
*.nii
*.nii.gz
*.NII
*.NII.GZ

# --- Phase-0 intake outputs (regulated store, never the repo) ---
# De-identified DICOM copies and the cohort provenance manifest. The
# manifest is PHI-free by construction (codename + geometry + labels),
# but a real-cohort manifest is still sensitive institutional data and
# belongs in the IRB store, not the public tree. Defense in depth.
*_deid/
**/*__QUARANTINE_FAILED/
cohort_manifest.csv
**/cohort_manifest.csv

# --- Runtime artefacts (may embed PHI) -------------------------
# Cached pipeline results carry the source DICOM header (PatientName,
# MRN, DOB, accession, institution). NONE of results/ is ever tracked.
results/
library/index.csv

# Derived renders from real patient CTs (segmentation / centerline
# figures). Development scratch — never tracked (same policy as results/).
output/

# --- PHI safety net: no .mat anywhere except synthetic phantoms -
# Defense in depth — every cached .mat (results/, .cache/, stray
# diagnostics) embeds the DICOM header. The only .mat that ships is the
# procedurally-generated phantom. A new cache file therefore CANNOT leak
# PHI by being forgotten in .gitignore.
*.mat
!library/PHANTOM_*.mat

# --- External-tool caches --------------------------------------
.cache/
.cache/**

# --- MATLAB ----------------------------------------------------
*.asv
*.m~
*.mex*
*.slxc
slprj/
sccprj/
codegen/
*.autosave
.matlab/

# --- macOS / editor noise --------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Python tooling envs ---------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.venv/
.python-version

# --- Build / docs artefacts ------------------------------------
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
docs/_build/

# --- Editor backups ---
*.bak
